ActTransportation of Dangerous Goods Act, 1992
SubjectVancouver 2010 Interim Order Respecting the Transportation of Dangerous Goods(into, through or Within Controlled Access Zones)
PrecisOrder approving the Vancouver 2010 Interim Order Respecting the Transportation of Dangerous Goods (Into, Through or Within Controlled Access Zones). The Interim Order is part of the safety and security plans for the 2010 Winter Olympics Games to be hosted in Vancouver, British Columbia, until the day on which the Olympics Athletes' Villages close.
